{"tid":1440690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再有高層離任 滙豐大中華CEO黃碧娟辭職 明日生效","createTime":"2019-08-10T13:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:07:35.000Z","uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ffb7d8ac931ff5b975eeb76c736567dbb928e7","tid":1440690,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190809/59915269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F59915269&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=ecaca08f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F59915269&h=b57154d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190809/59915269</a><br />\n<br />\n繼滙控（005）行政總裁范寧突然離職後，滙豐再有高層變動。消息透露，滙豐銀行副主席兼行政總裁王冬勝今日向大中華員工發出內部通訊，表示大中華行政總裁黃碧娟因尋求其他發展機會，明日起作離職前休假。據了解黃碧娟離開，與早前范寧辭職、集團全球裁員或華為事件並無關係，應該是她個人事業上有更佳發展。<br />\n<br />\n黃碧娟自1992年加入滙豐，在集團任職27年，目前掌管滙豐大中華業務，據悉她離開後，未必再安排另一高層接替其大中華行政總裁職位，而是由目前香港、中國、澳門及台灣的行政總裁，透過協作聯繫方式分擔原有職務。<br />\n<br />\n有d野"},{"pid":"dd38894c4c2f8ff8ca8fd59908f6372d94ebb2f2","tid":1440690,"uid":279000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩訓醒？"},{"pid":"79ea09c5d577fa1562090c049fdb10c90e8d1d9d","tid":1440690,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"但願佢地retirement後會爆大獲"},{"pid":"361c85214892c41e02e984a8fefbd080a0978b31","tid":1440690,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"訓得幾耐喎你都"}]}